{"tid":796854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(非強國) 【慎入●考車牌慘死】女學神停路軌畀火車撞死 考官急逃撿命","createTime":"2018-08-28T05:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T11:13:59.000Z","uid":53026,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"307cc8f9d3ac366b5c6beb4fba42e8732a867567","tid":796854,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"【慎入●考車牌慘死】女學神停路軌畀火車撞死 考官急逃撿命<br />\n\t<br />\n684<br />\n最後更新: 0828 12:53 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0828 12:38<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180828/large/1535429031_79e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180828%2Flarge%2F1535429031_79e0.jpg&h=7d4f7113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n    適中字型<br />\n    較大字型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180828&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58615333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180828%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58615333&h=01eb4579&s={SIZE}\" />\t<br />\n<br />\n【新增片段】<br />\n<br />\n波蘭一名少女考車牌時，突然將汽車停在一條路軌上，但少女走避不及遭火車撞死。目擊者透露，同車的考官及時逃離車廂，不過目擊者批評他沒協助救人。<br />\n<br />\n事發在波蘭南部，在鐵路附近的一部閉路電視拍下當時情況，可見一輛鈴木Baleno駛至火車路軌上突然停下，62歲考官及時離開，之後列車就直接撞上汽車。<br />\n<br />\n一名40歲目擊者表示：「當我們跑至殘骸時，那名少女被困，而考官就呆站在附近。我要他交一個急救箱給我，但他找不到。她仍然有呼吸的，但喘息越來越弱，就在我們眼前慢慢離開。」<br />\n<br />\n39歲目擊者又指，少女頭部受傷，身上佈滿血跡，「我們嘗試止血，我聽得到她粗重的呼吸聲」。另一人稱：「那名考官在最後一分鐘逃出來，那少女，很不幸沒有走出來。她有嘗試移動，僅差半米就有救了，她已經開始開車了。」這人又指火車已經在幾秒之前響號，但最終仍眼白白看着火車撞上汽車。<br />\n<br />\n警方指死者為18歲少女安杰莉卡（Angelika），捱撞後身體多處受傷，送院後不治，而火車司機及考牌官則沒有大礙，當局正調查今次意外。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"c52d6ee855360143bbcb6d6d3a2fadbe70cdfc33","tid":796854,"uid":52006,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"又係女人"},{"pid":"469541ee275b9cd63a5c721d9a4c6e7034f31f1d","tid":796854,"uid":49197,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"不過目擊者批評他沒協助救人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白痴?D火車咁撚快,就算想救都好難預救唔救倒架wo"},{"pid":"591e44fb4c014e050e05c35e1a32f010edf43486","tid":796854,"uid":53026,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"考官醒目"},{"pid":"4cb12b22ca83657deca848829a544366df26c61f","tid":796854,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb1ed14aa081b7d4849c206966af986f5a46de2","tid":796854,"uid":51436,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"469541ee275b9cd63a5c721d9a4c6e7034f31f1d","tid":796854,"uid":49197,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"不過目擊者批評他沒協助救人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白痴?D火車咁撚快,就算想救都好難預救唔救倒架wo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士無分國界"},{"pid":"b99f03427bfa0a815f3a2b3d3751f3b081dfa22e","tid":796854,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:23:44.000Z","msg":"女人渣車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d755bdea12a710082c7a3489a648a71256df8a5e","tid":796854,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"591e44fb4c014e050e05c35e1a32f010edf43486","tid":796854,"uid":53026,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"考官醒目"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:25:41.000Z","msg":"that bitch<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201608e787d63250ce8595efe567aca583da910f","tid":796854,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"女人揸車=？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03932cc3112b36d8674e664e1cfff1b99fad4a20","tid":796854,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"201608e787d63250ce8595efe567aca583da910f","tid":796854,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:03:08.000Z","m